674
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:57,710
Sir.

675
00:35:58,510 --> 00:35:59,920
What is the Young Lord playing at?

676
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,110
How should I know?

677
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:02,630
The Young Lord's intentions

678
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:04,000
