691
00:36:51,550 --> 00:36:52,880
Gu Dezhao.

692
00:36:53,110 --> 00:36:53,960
If you disown me,

693
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:55,440
I'll report you to the authorities!

694
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:57,880
Such a little girl,

695
00:36:58,110 --> 00:36:58,590
yet she really could

696
00:36:58,590 --> 00:36:59,710
ruin your official fortune?

697
00:37:00,480 --> 00:37:01,840
The prophecy from Priest Qingxu

698
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:02,840
cannot be false.

699
00:37:04,110 --> 00:37:04,590
Hurry!

700
00:37:05,070 --> 00:37:05,880
Tie her up,

701
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:06,840
