750
00:41:28,590 --> 00:41:29,320
But sir, I...

751
00:41:31,150 --> 00:41:31,760
What's wrong?

752
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:33,360
She burned her hand last night

753
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:34,550
