755
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:36,550
What...

756
00:41:41,710 --> 00:41:43,150
How could you be so careless?

757
00:41:43,150 --> 00:41:44,280
It really hurts.

758
00:41:46,440 --> 00:41:47,320
It's all red.

759
00:41:48,150 --> 00:41:48,710
Don't we have

760
00:41:48,710 --> 00:41:50,030
kitchen staff?

761
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:51,440
Why does a concubine

762
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,280
need to decoct medicine herself?

763
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:54,320
You don't know, Miss?

764
00:41:54,630 --> 00:41:55,920
Ever since Mrs. Gu fell ill,

765
00:41:56,440 --> 00:41:58,280
Ma'am has decocted

766
00:41:58,440 --> 00:42:00,030
