782
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:26,710
It's getting late.

783
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:27,880
All of you, go rest now.

784
00:42:31,550 --> 00:42:32,280
Good night, sir.

785
00:42:37,630 --> 00:42:38,440
Sister,

786
00:42:38,760 --> 00:42:40,400
you and the Young Lord

787
00:42:40,550 --> 00:42:41,960
must be very close, right?

788
00:42:42,710 --> 00:42:43,800
Not really close.

789
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:45,320
Just

790
00:42:45,670 --> 00:42:46,400
acquaintances.

791
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:48,360
Really?

792
00:42:48,710 --> 00:42:49,320
Then why would he

793
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:51,070
let you ride in the same carriage?

794
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:52,230
He's always been

795
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:54,030
extremely proud.

796
00:42:55,440 --> 00:42:56,510
I haven't even asked you yet,

797
00:42:56,510 --> 00:42:57,800
yet you question me first.

798
00:42:57,960 --> 00:42:59,360
You have quite a daughter!

799
00:42:59,480 --> 00:43:00,960
An unmarried young lady

800
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:02,360
riding back in a strange man's carriage.

801
00:43:02,550 --> 00:43:03,840
If word gets out,

802
00:43:04,150 --> 00:43:05,190
where is

803
00:43:05,190 --> 00:43:06,320
my dignity?

804
00:43:06,670 --> 00:43:07,710
Jinzhao said

805
00:43:08,230 --> 00:43:09,400
the carriage broke down.

806
00:43:10,190 --> 00:43:10,760
Broke down?

807
00:43:10,920 --> 00:43:12,230
She could have sent someone for help,

808
00:43:12,230 --> 00:43:13,670
and waited for us to send a carriage!

809
00:43:14,110 --> 00:43:15,670
She did it on purpose!

810
00:43:15,920 --> 00:43:16,800
She rode back in

811
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:18,000
the Young Lord's carriage

812
00:43:18,190 --> 00:43:19,190
just to make me, her father,

813
00:43:19,190 --> 00:43:19,920
kneel to her

814
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:20,880
and make a fool of myself.

815
00:43:21,630 --> 00:43:23,230
How can you say that about Jinzhao?

816
00:43:26,110 --> 00:43:27,440
Pay no mind to it.

817
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:28,760
Sir and Madam fight like this

818
00:43:28,760 --> 00:43:30,000
all the time.

819
00:43:30,150 --> 00:43:31,030
I'm used to it.

820
00:43:32,630 --> 00:43:33,480
Let's go.

821
00:43:33,880 --> 00:43:34,280
This way.

822
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:40,550
Nanny Zhou was obviously stirring trouble.

823
00:43:41,030 --> 00:43:42,280
As the mistress of the household,

824
00:43:42,760 --> 00:43:44,110
she didn't see it at all.

825
00:43:45,320 --> 00:43:46,320
No wonder it sounded

826
00:43:46,320 --> 00:43:47,510
so wrong to me.

827
00:43:48,150 --> 00:43:49,150
Now that you mention it,

828
00:43:49,400 --> 00:43:50,510
I see it clearly.

829
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:51,760
That Nanny Zhou

830
00:43:51,880 --> 00:43:52,920
did it deliberately.

831
00:43:53,230 --> 00:43:54,030
She knew full well

832
00:43:54,030 --> 00:43:55,550
Gu Dezhao was angry

833
00:43:55,760 --> 00:43:56,710
about the Young Lord,

834
00:43:57,030 --> 00:43:58,150
and she still brought up the carriage

835
00:43:58,320 --> 00:43:59,230
